      "strategic_advice": "When you see words like **'neither'** or activities ending in **'-ing'**, remember they act as singular subjects and need a singular verb.\n- For question tags, if the sentence has a negative word like **'rarely'** or **'never'**, always use a positive tag!\n- Read the sentence quietly to yourself to see if the tense sounds right with the time clues given.",
      "trigger_keywords": [
        "neither",
        "rarely",
        "-ing words"
